          div  &#xE05A;
          div Calculate pulmonary artery pulsatility index (PAPi)
          div &#xE003;&#xE069; Studied to predict RVAD need in LVAD patients
          div &#xE003;&#xE069; PAPi = (systolic PA pressure - diastolic PA pressure) / CVP
          div  &#xE04F;
          div PAPi &gt;2: good RV function
          div  &#xE04F;
          div PAPi 1-2: at risk for RV failure
          div  &#xE04F;
          div PAPi &lt;1: RV failure
          div  &#xE05A;
