          div catheters see page 125.
          div Management
          div 1.  Prevent elevated pulmonary vascular resistance
          div a.  Avoid hypoxemia, hypercapnia, and acidosis which increase PVR
          div 2.  Optimize preload
          div a.  Fluid Administration
